{"tid":1052224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被問「付多少錢可以X你」 激怒AV女優這樣回","createTime":"2019-03-08T06:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T08:09:10.000Z","uid":25345,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ba8bdd5c1ce1b92266ff739772c47de5d801ebd2","tid":1052224,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:58:12.000Z","msg":"25歲日本AV女優川越唯入行6年，累積不少死忠粉絲，近日她在推特上透露，以前的同學傳訊息問她，「付多少錢可以X你」，讓她非常火大，粉絲看到後也表示「太過份。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n川越唯在推特PO文表示，日前有一名交情不錯的同學，突然傳LINE問她說，「請問付你多少錢，你願意和我啪啪啪？」讓川越唯動怒，感覺對方看不起AV女優這個行業，她想不通怎麼會有人這樣說話，也呼籲大家千萬別跟認識的AV女優說這種話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粉絲看到後心疼她，紛紛表示，「真的有慾望，怎麼不直接去風俗店就好？」「應該反問給多少錢可以捅他菊花」、「這要求太不合理了，就算是朋友也不該開這種尷尬的玩笑」。"},{"pid":"d334e9636e877e49e31ebccc24e4dac881cf3bfb","tid":1052224,"uid":78347,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"退休之後咪又係去風俗店撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係雞需要分得咁仔細嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9362383567416bbde5e663c47ac43940a9f4d14","tid":1052224,"uid":122134,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/b13863464534534o26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fb13863464534534o26.png&h=e55dcf0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aed1086ecab1fe9f7759ab63ebee722cad2382e2","tid":1052224,"uid":136760,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:01:12.000Z","msg":"全相都睇過啦 比錢你賺都唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d0c7b733009f786ff77d192a2e5eabd5c0f64b","tid":1052224,"uid":111814,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:04:11.000Z","msg":"應該問: 請問付你多少錢，你才願意和我一起拍AV呢？<br />\n咁先